## COMPONENT OWNERSHIP

Each agent session should own exactly one component. Do not scope-creep.

| Component | Owner file(s) |
|-----------|--------------|
| 8080 Emulator core | `src/emu/cpu.c`, `src/emu/cpu.h` |
| Memory / Tape | `src/emu/mem.c`, `src/emu/mem.h` |
| BIOS & I/O | `src/bios/bios.c`, `src/bios/bios.h` |
| Kernel FSM | `src/kernel/kernel.c`, `src/kernel/kernel.h` |
| Filesystem (CP/M-like) | `src/fs/fs.c`, `src/fs/fs.h` |
| Shell | `src/shell/shell.c`, `src/shell/shell.h` |
| Tiny C Compiler | `src/compiler/compiler.c`, `src/compiler/compiler.h` |
| Test Suite | `tests/` |
| Pygame Visualizer | `viz/visualizer.py`, `viz/tape_bridge.py` |
| Build / Docker | `Makefile`, `Dockerfile`, `docker-compose.yml` |

